'''S'kytric''' was the native language of the [[S'kytri]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Skye/Legends|Skye]].

S'kytric had been considered a dead language until it became the basis of a folk revival due to its use by musicians and artists.

Most S'kytri were fluent in both S'kytric and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.

